General Information

Blackstrap Molasses is a natural source of minerals including calcium, magnesium, iron and manganese.

Warnings

Caution: Some people may find that Molasses has a mild laxative effect.

Common Uses

Blackstrap Molasses can be substituted for honey or golden syrup in many recipes. It can also be dissolved in hot water and stirred into drinks.

Ingredients

100% Blackstrap Molasses. Seasonal variation may occur. Preservative free, no slphur added.

Directions

Suggested serving size: 10m/14g
